{"tid":2141020,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：香港民研：習評分包尾  遠低於朱鎔基 - 李八方","createTime":"2020-08-05T11:25:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T11:28:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f3907d76a33d1987301e44db3e0feee0d6215e78","tid":2141020,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:25:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200805/6TNG56M4KTFX36UG7AJ2RITV24/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200805%2F6TNG56M4KTFX36UG7AJ2RITV24%2F&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2F%2BNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=e5c9d291\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200805%2F6TNG56M4KTFX36UG7AJ2RITV24%2F&h=f8b5ae8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200805/6TNG56M4KTFX36UG7AJ2RITV24/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：香港民研：習評分包尾 <br />\n遠低於朱鎔基 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Hh95TQYcFbaZcG4L3JdiS3dfQ_k=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CJECC4IISGKISAZMTKVHVD7SYI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHh95TQYcFbaZcG4L3JdiS3dfQ_k%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCJECC4IISGKISAZMTKVHVD7SYI.jpg&h=690f5198&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共國家主席習近平唔止喺中共政權上稱帝，連香港民研公佈最新十大兩岸政治人物嘅調查報告亦顯示，佢喺中國政治人物入面亦成功攞第一，不過係倒數第一。 香港民研喺本月20至24日就兩岸領導人評分，訪問咗1,024名港人，結果發現習總只得40.7分，而多次發表公開演說支持港人嘅台灣總統蔡英文就有57.6分，大幅拋離習總16.9分，連已退下火線多年嘅中共前總理朱鎔基都有61.6分，高過習總20.9分。<br />\n<br />\n根據香港民研調查結果，。。。。。。。。。。，但蔡嘅評分就高過習總多多聲啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鍾劍華：港人懷念逝去歲月<br />\n<br />\n究竟點解自詡為21世紀毛澤東嘅習總，會輸咗畀蔡英文同朱鎔基呢？。。。。。。。。。。。。，更顯示出「香港人都好懷念逝去咗嘅歲月」。"},{"pid":"35d337caffd55663423aef8a57c4f7c69bf3fc25","tid":2141020,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:28:45.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}